entry.value: select student_attendance_no_schools(${hd:substringAfter('|')},${hd:substringBefore('|')}); insert into student_attendance_exception_agg as a (school_id,year,month,school_name,block_id,block_name,district_id,district_name,cluster_id,cluster_name, school_latitude,school_longitude,district_latitude,district_longitude,block_latitude,block_longitude,cluster_latitude,cluster_longitude,school_management_type,school_category, created_on,updated_on) select school_id,year,month,school_name,block_id,block_name,district_id,district_name,cluster_id,cluster_name, school_latitude,school_longitude,district_latitude,district_longitude,block_latitude,block_longitude,cluster_latitude,cluster_longitude, school_management_type,'overall' as school_category,now(),now() from student_attendance_exception_data on conflict (school_id,month,year) do update set school_id=excluded.school_id,school_name=excluded.school_name,year=excluded.year,month=excluded.month,block_id=excluded.block_id, block_name=excluded.block_name,cluster_id=excluded.cluster_id,cluster_name=excluded.cluster_name,district_id=excluded.district_id,district_name=excluded.district_name, school_latitude=excluded.school_latitude,school_longitude=excluded.school_longitude,cluster_latitude=excluded.cluster_latitude, cluster_longitude=excluded.cluster_longitude,block_latitude=excluded.block_latitude,block_longitude=excluded.block_longitude,district_latitude=excluded.district_latitude, district_longitude=excluded.district_longitude,created_on=excluded.created_on,school_management_type=excluded.school_management_type,school_category=excluded.school_category,updated_on=now();
